thread.title: BRIEF-Dohia Group unit to set up internet culture related JV with partner

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Dohia Group unit to set up internet culture related JV with partner
text:
Jan 22(Reuters) - Dohia Group Co Ltd
* Says coâ€™s Beijing-based wholly owned network technology unit signs agreement with an individual (partner), to jointly set up an internet culture related JV
* Says unit and partner will invest 3 million yuan and 2 million yuan in the JV respectively
* Says unit and partner will hold a 60 percent stake and a 40 percent stake in the JV respectively
